[101.148442, "o", "Scheduled Meeting: Wednesday, January 17, 2024, 11:00 AM - 12:00 PM UTC\r\n\r\nAlice's Constraints:\r\n  - Available: 9 AM - 2 PM only\r\n  - Busy: Mon 10-11 AM, Mon 1-2 PM, Tue 10 AM-12 PM, Wed 10-11 AM, Wed 1-2 PM, Thu 10-11 AM, Fri 10-11 AM, Fri 1-2 PM\r\n  - Meeting time 11 AM-12 PM: Within 9 AM-2 PM ✓\r\n  - No conflict with Wed 10-11 AM meeting ✓\r\n\r\nBob's Constraints:\r\n  - No meetings before 10 AM\r\n  - Must leave by 4:30 PM on Tue/Thu\r\n  - Busy: Mon 11 AM-12 PM, Mon 1-3 PM, Tue 1-2 PM, Wed 12-1 PM, Thu 1-2 PM, Fri 12-1 PM\r\n  - Meeting time 11 AM-12 PM: After 10 AM ✓\r\n  - No conflict with Wed 12-1 PM meeting ✓\r\n\r\nCarol's Constraints:\r\n"]
[101.148748, "o", "  - Available: 9 AM - 5 PM\r\n  - Lunch break: 12:00-12:30 PM (unavailable)\r\n  - Prefers not Monday\r\n  - Busy: Mon 11 AM-12 PM, Tue 11 AM-12 PM, Tue 1-2 PM, Wed 12-1 PM, Thu 12-1 PM, Fri 11 AM-12 PM\r\n  - Meeting time 11 AM-12 PM: Within 9 AM-5 PM ✓\r\n  - No conflict with lunch (12:00-12:30 PM) ✓\r\n  - Not Monday ✓\r\n  - No conflict with Wed 12-1 PM meeting ✓\r\n\r\nEarliest Slot Analysis:\r\n  Monday 1/15:\r\n    - 9-10 AM: Alice free, Bob can't (before 10 AM), Carol free → INVALID\r\n    - 10-11 AM: Alice busy, Bob busy (11 AM-12 PM overlaps), Carol busy → INVALID\r\n    - 11 AM-12 PM: Alice free, Bob busy, Carol busy → INVALID\r\n    - 12-1 PM: Alice free, Bob free, Carol lunch break (12:00-12:30) → INVALID\r\n    - 1-2 PM: Alice busy, Bob busy, Carol free → INVALID\r\n  Tuesday 1/16:\r\n    - 10-11 AM: Alice busy (10 AM-12 PM), Bob free, Carol free → INVALID\r\n    - 11 AM-12 PM: Alice busy (10 AM-12 PM), Bob free, Carol busy → INVALID\r\n    - 12-1 PM: Alice free, Bob free, Carol lunch break (12:00-12:30) → INVALID\r\n    - 1-2 PM: Alice free, Bob busy, Carol busy → INVALID\r\n  Wednesday 1/17:\r\n    - 10-11 AM: Alice busy, Bob free, Carol free → INVALID\r\n    - 11 AM-12 PM: Alice free, Bob free, Carol free → VALID ✓✓✓\r\n\r\nResult: Wednesday, Jan 17, 11 AM-12 PM is the EARLIEST valid slot!\r\n"]
